== 2...d5 ==
Black puts their pawn in the centre. Play can transpose into the '''Paulsen variation''' after '''[[/3. d4/]]''' or the '''Two-knights''' after '''[[/3. Nf3/]]'''.

'''[[/3. exd5/]]''' transposes into the exchange French, but is somewhat inaccurate due to the knight blocking the c3-pawn, which would usually support the d4-pawn.

